OL,6,FWATCH: Bodycam footage shows the
OL,7,Fmoment a thief wields a crowbar at
OL,8,Fpolice officers during an armed robbery
OL,10,FBodycam footage has captured the
OL,11,Fmoment a thief armed with a weapon
OL,12,Fcharged at police officers during a
OL,13,Frobbery in Kent.
OL,15,FTwo men forced their way into a shop
OL,16,Fin New Ash Green using crowbars on 22
OL,17,FNovember 2024.
OL,19,FCallum Knox and Damian Smith broke
OL,20,Finto a Morrisons store in The Row,
OL,21,Fwearing balaclavas, at around 1:40am.
