OL,6,FTwo Kent police officers raced to the
OL,7,Fscene after an intruder alert was
OL,8,Ftriggered.
OL,10,FA member of shop staff was challenging
OL,11,Fthe Knox and Smith, when the officers
OL,12,Frushed inside.
OL,14,FSmith surrendered, dropped his crowbar
OL,15,Fand lay on the floor, when asked to by
OL,16,Fthe police.
OL,18,FKnox attempted to escape, and with a
OL,19,Fcrowbar raised above his head, ran
OL,20,Ftowards an exit and one of the
OL,21,Fofficers.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/5
