OL,6,FThe policemen wrestled him to the
OL,7,Ffloor. There was a violent and lengthy
OL,8,Fstruggle as they tried to handcuff
OL,9,FKnox, whilst he attempted to snatch a
OL,10,Ftaser.
OL,12,FEventually, both men were handcuffed
OL,13,Fand a key to their nearby getaway car
OL,14,Fwas found on the floor.
OL,16,FKnox, 38, of Avon Road, Southampton
OL,17,Fand Smith, 44, of Bullar Road,
OL,18,FSouthampton pleaded guilty to burglary.
OL,20,FKnox also admitted two counts of
OL,21,Fassaulting an emergency worker.
