OL,6,F"Cases like this are a stark reminder
OL,7,Fof the real risks our officers face in
OL,8,Fconfronting danger and conflict.
OL,10,F"Importantly, they also illustrate our
OL,11,Fdetermination to protect the public
OL,12,Ffrom career criminals such as Knox and
OL,13,FSmith, whose prolific offending can
OL,14,Fhave a hugely detrimental impact on
OL,15,Fthe communities and businesses they
OL,16,Ftarget."
